name: chaos party
description:
when the world just crumpled down around you, night is still young and the party is getting too wild until you dont have a chance just to vent and rant a little bit in a mean time. your mind start to break down and get a bit hazy, almost done about all your life.

nah. this artwork is just about taking a breath from reality. 
---------------------------
this is my second drop. i wish that we all stay healthy, physical and our mental health. support for each other and who does seek for help. sometimes, the world is just getting messed up more and more.

thank you for your appreciate. hope you enjoy my artwork. XOXO
